sold to a distant Landowner,

269
00:19:21,223 --> 00:19:22,646
they panicked.

270
00:19:22,646 --> 00:19:25,313
(woman screams)

271
00:19:27,467 --> 00:19:30,970
The thought of being
removed from their families

272
00:19:30,970 --> 00:19:33,085
and their homes was much more
than they could understand

273
00:19:33,085 --> 00:19:33,918
or accept.

274
00:19:36,377 --> 00:19:39,720
The strongest broke
through the chain fence.

275
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:42,263
And in their stampede to run for freedom,

276
00:19:42,263 --> 00:19:43,954
you apprehended them.

277
00:19:43,954 --> 00:19:44,787
All 37.

278
00:19:46,295 --> 00:19:48,521
They were trampled to death.

279
00:19:48,521 --> 00:19:49,708
Men and women.

280
00:19:49,708 --> 00:19:53,541
But what we can never
forget are the children.

281
00:19:55,722 --> 00:19:57,222
37 trampled, dead.

282
00:19:59,702 --> 00:20:01,168
- [Landowner] That wasn't my fault.

283
00:20:01,168 --> 00:20:03,469
- You caused their deaths.

284
00:20:03,469 --> 00:20:07,527
We hold you totally responsible for this.

285
00:20:07,527 --> 00:20:08,682
- Lies.

286
00:20:08,682 --> 00:20:10,141
I'm not guilty.

287
00:20:10,141 --> 00:20:11,507
Anything I've done.

288
00:20:11,507 --> 00:20:13,238
Not at all, not at all.

289
00:20:13,238 --> 00:20:14,280
I'm not guilty!

290
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:15,320
They're lies!

291
00:20:15,320 --> 00:20:17,308
- We will judge you
for your transgressions

292
00:20:17,308 --> 00:20:20,338
and misdeeds, not only against myself,

293
00:20:20,338 --> 00:20:23,000
but against the other who have suffered

294
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:26,109
under the yoke of bondage
and inhumanities committed

295
00:20:26,109 --> 00:20:28,787
upon us in your household.

296
00:20:28,787 --> 00:20:32,438
You will be tried for
your personal injustices

297
00:20:32,438 --> 00:20:33,605
and cruelties.

298
00:20:34,914 --> 00:20:38,175
And if my lady jurors so
find you to be guilty,

299
00:20:38,175 --> 00:20:40,941
executed in a manner that
they choose to be fitting.

300
00:20:40,941 --> 00:20:43,093
- [Court Members] Yes, yes!

301
00:20:43,093 --> 00:20:47,260
- But first, my jurors
shall introduce themselves.

302
00:20:49,229 --> 00:20:50,760
- Butra.

303
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:51,690
- Suhya.

304
00:20:51,690 --> 00:20:52,690
- Sellahlie.

305
00:20:54,759 --> 00:20:56,500
- Fleurlilli.

306
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:57,333
- Etrosef.

307
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:00,317
- Wishtofti.

308
00:21:00,317 --> 00:21:01,891
- Petrinah.

309
00:21:01,891 --> 00:21:03,497
- Belahsa.

310
00:21:03,497 --> 00:21:04,414
- Raybutta.

311
00:21:08,753 --> 00:21:12,318
- And have you ladies of the
jury chosen a spokesperson?

312
00:21:12,318 --> 00:21:13,151
- Yes!
- Yes, we have.

313
00:21:13,151 --> 00:21:14,477
- Yes!

314
00:21:14,477 --> 00:21:18,872
- Yes, we have chosen Butra
to be our spokeswoman.

315
00:21:18,872 --> 00:21:20,122
- Butra, Butra.

316
00:21:21,547 --> 00:21:23,938
- Yes, Your Majesty?

317
00:21:23,938 --> 00:21:28,105
I would rather have been
selected as his executioner.

318
00:21:29,341 --> 00:21:31,008
But then, who knows?

319
00:21:34,430 --> 00:21:35,413
(Landowner grunts)

320
00:21:35,413 --> 00:21:36,978
- Maybe I will be.

321
00:21:36,978 --> 00:21:39,745
- Maybe we will all be his executioners,

322
00:21:39,745 --> 00:21:41,702
should he be found guilty.

323
00:21:41,702 --> 00:21:44,974
Have you decided the manner
in which he is to stand trial?

324
00:21:44,974 --> 00:21:47,024
- [Butra] Yes, we have, Your Majesty.

325
00:21:47,024 --> 00:21:49,638
- [Wateesa] And what manner will it be?

326
00:21:49,638 --> 00:21:53,805
- We have decided that he
will lie down on the floor,

327
00:21:54,913 --> 00:21:55,913
on his back!

328
00:21:56,780 --> 00:22:01,467
With Your Majesty's feet
pressed into pit of his stomach.

329
00:22:01,467 --> 00:22:02,667
(Landowner grunts)

330
00:22:02,667 --> 00:22:05,047
As it was with you in your childhood.

331
00:22:05,047 --> 00:22:08,400
As for for the rest of us,
we will place our chairs

332
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,317
around him!

333
00:22:10,499 --> 00:22:13,166
And press his back to the floor.

334
00:22:14,430 --> 00:22:18,430
Under our shoe, he and
what he represents to us,

335
00:22:20,056 --> 00:22:23,556
deserves to be treated as dirt beneath us.

336
00:22:25,101 --> 00:22:26,434
- [Jurors] Yeah!

337
00:22:29,299 --> 00:22:34,184
- [Woman] And if he tongue is
loose, our kicks may find him.

338
00:22:34,184 --> 00:22:36,767
(jurors chide)

339
00:22:42,183 --> 00:22:44,598
- [Wateesah] So be it.

340
00:22:44,598 --> 00:22:47,765
- [Landowner] You can't do this to me.

341
00:22:50,058 --> 00:22:52,391
- [Butra] Now, on your back!

342
00:22:53,479 --> 00:22:54,312
Now!

343
00:22:55,542 --> 00:22:57,365
Or you're going down,

344
00:22:57,365 --> 00:22:58,203
a-kicking.

345
00:22:58,203 --> 00:23:02,495
(Landowner breathes heavily)

346
00:23:02,495 --> 00:23:04,745
- Yes, strangely befitting.

347
00:23:06,495 --> 00:23:09,897
The shoe is on the other foot, now.

348
00:23:09,897 --> 00:23:12,543
When we as children,
according to your custom,

349
00:23:12,543 --> 00:23:16,710
lay down on our backs, under
your cold and unfeeling feet.

350
00:23:19,377 --> 00:23:23,544
Which were pressed in the pit
of our warm little bellies.

351
00:23:25,292 --> 00:23:28,787
We were used to absorb
the pain and afflictions

352
00:23:28,787 --> 00:23:32,678
from your body, the cold
deadly, transmitting your pain

353
00:23:32,678 --> 00:23:33,511
to us.

354
00:23:36,142 --> 00:23:39,775
The only pain I remember
was once as a child.

355
00:23:39,775 --> 00:23:43,681
You were in a hurry to stand,
and you did not first remove

356
00:23:43,681 --> 00:23:45,848
your feet from my stomach.

357
00:23:46,985 --> 00:23:51,057
Your full weight upon my
tiny body forced the air

358
00:23:51,057 --> 00:23:55,239
from my lungs, and my
mouth filled with the food

359
00:23:55,239 --> 00:23:56,572
from my stomach.

360
00:23:58,411 --> 00:24:01,648
Your body is much bigger
and stronger as mine was

361
00:24:01,648 --> 00:24:02,565
as a child.

362
00:24:04,661 --> 00:24:08,328
Perhaps, the sharp heels
of my shoes pressed

363
00:24:09,745 --> 00:24:12,554
against your body will
make up the difference,

364
00:24:12,554 --> 00:24:17,169
should I choose to stand
upon you as you did me,

365
00:24:17,169 --> 00:24:18,002
you pig.

366
00:24:19,682 --> 00:24:22,182
Let us proceed with the trial.

367
00:24:23,095 --> 00:24:26,044
Let us first take an oath.

368
00:24:26,044 --> 00:24:29,507
Do you as jurors swear
that the testimony you are

369
00:24:29,507 --> 00:24:33,838
about to give, and the
charges you are about to make,

370
00:24:33,838 --> 00:24:37,421
are true as seen or
witnessed by your eyes,

371
00:24:38,361 --> 00:24:40,766
and not the hearsay of others?

372
00:24:40,766 --> 00:24:42,003
- [Jurors] Yes.

373
00:24:42,003 --> 00:24:43,241
- Yes.

374
00:24:43,241 --> 00:24:46,074
Let's proceed with the trial then.

375
00:24:47,910 --> 00:24:48,743
Butra.

376
00:24:50,131 --> 00:24:52,714
You may start with the charges.

377
00:24:55,084 --> 00:24:58,501
- First, let me say that this evil person

378
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:04,710
branded my man with the r for run away.

379
00:25:08,827 --> 00:25:10,577
Then, had him killed.

380
00:25:25,371 --> 00:25:27,515
- Call upon the others for their charges.

381
00:25:27,515 --> 00:25:29,486
- Yes, Your Majesty.

382
00:25:29,486 --> 00:25:32,751
- You know, you know I'm
not guilty of these things.

383
00:25:32,751 --> 00:25:35,602
I have done nothing, nothing like that.

384
00:25:35,602 --> 00:25:36,525
They're lies!

385
00:25:36,525 --> 00:25:39,025
(jurors yell)

386
00:25:39,943 --> 00:25:40,776
- Stop!

387
00:25:41,622 --> 00:25:45,792
Stop, sit down, save it for
until the trial is complete,

388
00:25:45,792 --> 00:25:48,893
and sentence has been passed.

389
00:25:48,893 --> 00:25:49,889
- [Landowner] Sentence for what?

390
00:25:49,889 --> 00:25:52,639
What do you mean passed sentence?

391
00:25:54,162 --> 00:25:58,280
- Butra, now do you have
witnesses for these charges?

392
00:25:58,280 --> 00:26:00,006
- Yes, Your Majesty.

393
00:26:00,006 --> 00:26:04,842
I will now call upon
FLeurlilli for her testimony.

394
00:26:04,842 --> 00:26:06,101
- No, no, please.

395
00:26:06,101 --> 00:26:09,184
Keep her away from me, keep her away.

396
00:26:10,671 --> 00:26:14,171
- My mother was enslaved by this very man.

397
00:26:15,693 --> 00:26:17,026
At an early age.

398
00:26:18,028 --> 00:26:20,687
And I was born in the fields.

399
00:26:20,687 --> 00:26:24,520
Then, one day, this very
man brought my mother

400
00:26:26,418 --> 00:26:31,144
into his household, and made
her into his personal slave.

401
00:26:31,144 --> 00:26:34,977
Cooking and cleaning,
from sun up to sun down.

402
00:26:36,151 --> 00:26:38,605
She had no life of her own.

403
00:26:38,605 --> 00:26:42,438
I saw her lie down and
die, a tired old woman.

404
00:26:43,447 --> 00:26:46,797
As long as she was alive
to keep me from you,

405
00:26:46,797 --> 00:26:49,207
I was barely a slave.

406
00:26:49,207 --> 00:26:51,874
But when mamma died, he used me.

407
00:26:53,117 --> 00:26:56,548
(ominous music)

408
00:26:56,548 --> 00:26:59,798
I was beaten half to death by this man.

409
00:27:01,973 --> 00:27:04,813
I was so scared that he would kill me

410
00:27:04,813 --> 00:27:07,480
if I didn't give into his wants.

411
00:27:09,703 --> 00:27:12,417
I charge this man with enslavement.

412
00:27:12,417 --> 00:27:16,190
I charge you with sexual
molestation of my mind, body

413
00:27:16,190 --> 00:27:17,043
and person.

414
00:27:17,043 --> 00:27:19,971
(Landowner groans)

415
00:27:19,971 --> 00:27:22,147
I charge this man with continuous rape!

416
00:27:22,147 --> 00:27:25,064
(Landowner groans)

417
00:27:28,143 --> 00:27:30,532
I would enslave him.

418
00:27:30,532 --> 00:27:33,911
I would cut off his private parts!

419
00:27:33,911 --> 00:27:35,232
- [Landowner] Oh, no, no.

420
00:27:35,232 --> 00:27:37,956
- I'd work him and work him!

421
00:27:37,956 --> 00:27:39,039
And work him!

422
00:27:40,733 --> 00:27:43,650
He would feel the sting of my whip!

423
00:27:45,587 --> 00:27:49,170
I would whip him and
whip him and whip him!

424
00:27:51,230 --> 00:27:54,813
Until death would
relieve him of his agony!

425
00:27:58,239 --> 00:28:01,060
- Thank you for your sworn
testimony, FLeurlilli.

426
00:28:01,060 --> 00:28:05,154
- I would now call upon, for
the last of our testimony,

427
00:28:05,154 --> 00:28:05,987
Belahsa.

428
00:28:05,987 --> 00:28:09,454
(thunder cracks)

429
00:28:09,454 --> 00:28:13,458
- When I was very small, your
people came to the field.

430
00:28:13,458 --> 00:28:17,987
They chose me to be a
slave in your household.

431
00:28:17,987 --> 00:28:19,904
I screamed and I cried.

432
00:28:22,130 --> 00:28:23,808
I didn't want to be away from my mother,

433
00:28:23,808 --> 00:28:25,808
my brothers and sisters.

434
00:28:26,705 --> 00:28:30,758
They took me by the hair
and they dragged me.

435
00:28:30,758 --> 00:28:31,841
But my uncle,

436
00:28:33,811 --> 00:28:36,810
my beloved uncle with
his beautiful love for me

437
00:28:36,810 --> 00:28:38,635
didn't want to see me taken to the field,

438
00:28:38,635 --> 00:28:40,175
to the mansion.

439
00:28:40,175 --> 00:28:42,804
To this man's mansion!

440
00:28:42,804 --> 00:28:44,094
- But I didn't hurt you.

441
00:28:44,094 --> 00:28:45,499
- He begged them.

442
00:28:45,499 --> 00:28:46,454
He pulled on their arms, he pleaded

443
00:28:46,454 --> 00:28:49,165
with them not to take me.

444
00:28:49,165 --> 00:28:53,332
Until they hit him and knocked
him stiff into the ground.

445
00:28:55,346 --> 00:28:59,174
They beat him with whips,
and then when one tired,

446
00:28:59,174 --> 00:29:00,924
the others took over.

447
00:29:02,307 --> 00:29:05,109
When he tried to cover
and protect himself,

448
00:29:05,109 --> 00:29:08,344
they whipped him for doing it!

449
00:29:08,344 --> 00:29:10,511
They whipped him to death!

450
00:29:13,207 --> 00:29:14,730
- [Landowner] I didn't
do it, my men did it.

451
00:29:14,730 --> 00:29:18,691
- For years, I couldn't erase
this vision from my memory.

452
00:29:18,691 --> 00:29:23,041
I worked and slaved for
you, yet I hated you

453
00:29:23,041 --> 00:29:25,291
for the murder of my uncle!

454
00:29:26,126 --> 00:29:28,496
Ah, with this whip,

455
00:29:28,496 --> 00:29:31,079
I could slay you alive, mister.

456
00:29:32,381 --> 00:29:35,397
I would whip you until the leather was red

457
00:29:35,397 --> 00:29:38,868
with your blood and your
breath stopped blowing

458
00:29:38,868 --> 00:29:40,110
within you.

459
00:29:40,110 --> 00:29:43,081
(Landowner chokes)

460
00:29:43,081 --> 00:29:45,164
I hate your guts, Master.

461
00:29:47,347 --> 00:29:49,802
And when my arms gave
out from whipping you,

462
00:29:49,802 --> 00:29:52,052
my sisters would take over.

463
00:29:53,092 --> 00:29:56,342
I charge you with cruelty, enslavement,

464
00:29:57,507 --> 00:29:59,757
and the murder of my uncle!

465
00:30:01,666 --> 00:30:05,480
I would beat you dead for your crimes.

466
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:07,348
- And I, likewise,

467
00:30:07,348 --> 00:30:11,371
would see this man blind and run to death.

468
00:30:11,371 --> 00:30:13,954
And that death may be his fate.

469
00:30:22,740 --> 00:30:26,907
- I will now call upon
Raybutta for her testimony.

470
00:30:32,244 --> 00:30:35,077
- My fellow jurors, I saw this man

471
00:30:39,327 --> 00:30:41,244
kill a 19-year-old boy!

472
00:30:45,749 --> 00:30:46,582
19!

473
00:30:49,271 --> 00:30:50,104
Why?

474
00:30:52,120 --> 00:30:54,870
Because his wife, she wanted him!

475
00:30:57,220 --> 00:31:00,637
She wanted his body pressed against hers!

476
00:31:01,944 --> 00:31:04,276
And then he refused!

477
00:31:04,276 --> 00:31:05,193
He refused!

478
00:31:07,931 --> 00:31:11,431
So, he came to back door, and he made him,

479
00:31:13,885 --> 00:31:16,635
made him confess to touching her!

480
00:31:19,625 --> 00:31:22,150
(Landowner grunts)

481
00:31:22,150 --> 00:31:22,983
I saw him!

482
00:31:24,959 --> 00:31:25,792
I saw him!

483
00:31:27,276 --> 00:31:31,443
He took and dragged and
beat this 19-year-old boy.

484
00:31:33,212 --> 00:31:35,212
He covered him with tar.

485
00:31:37,233 --> 00:31:39,150
And then he burned him.

486
00:31:40,464 --> 00:31:42,047
- Help, help, help!

487
00:31:43,548 --> 00:31:44,775
- Kill him!

488
00:31:44,775 --> 00:31:45,967
(jurors yell)

489
00:31:45,967 --> 00:31:47,908
(landowner gasps)

490
00:31:47,908 --> 00:31:49,491
- Stop it, stop it!

491
00:31:58,110 --> 00:32:03,075
- I will now call upon
Petrinah for her testimony.

492
00:32:03,075 --> 00:32:05,742
(Thunder rolls)

493
00:32:14,331 --> 00:32:15,498
- I, Petrinah,

494
00:32:19,108 --> 00:32:22,025
charge you, an enemy of my country,

495
00:32:25,878 --> 00:32:27,961
with the acts of treason!

496
00:32:29,639 --> 00:32:34,190
With the acts of brutality
against my people!

497
00:32:34,190 --> 00:32:36,523
Acts of murder, enslavement!

498
00:32:40,220 --> 00:32:44,330
Some of our meager cash
resources with our purses

499
00:32:44,330 --> 00:32:46,663
recovered from your baggage.

500
00:32:47,921 --> 00:32:51,821
These acts against each and
every one of us present.

501
00:32:51,821 --> 00:32:54,457
Will he draw execution
if they were perpetrated

502
00:32:54,457 --> 00:32:56,319
against your people?

503
00:32:56,319 --> 00:32:57,402
By any of us?

504
00:32:58,650 --> 00:33:01,647
Your court would convict and execute us

505
00:33:01,647 --> 00:33:03,454
without any hesitation.

506
00:33:03,454 --> 00:33:05,121
For these same acts.

507
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:08,320
I'm witness to your crimes.

508
00:33:09,862 --> 00:33:13,190
I'm witness to your years of infamy.

509
00:33:13,190 --> 00:33:15,690
Those things are unforgivable.

510
00:33:17,014 --> 00:33:19,181
There must be a vengeance.

511
00:33:20,631 --> 00:33:22,214
And eye for an eye.

512
00:33:23,619 --> 00:33:25,286
A tooth for a tooth.

513
00:33:27,033 --> 00:33:28,533
A life for a life.

514
00:33:30,077 --> 00:33:32,701
I say death for you now!

515
00:33:32,701 --> 00:33:34,233
Death for you now!

516
00:33:34,233 --> 00:33:35,869
At the hands of this court.

517
00:33:35,869 --> 00:33:38,786
(Landowner groans)

518
00:33:43,147 --> 00:33:46,730
- You can't mean this,
you can't mean this.

519
00:33:47,710 --> 00:33:49,715
- Please, please.

520
00:33:49,715 --> 00:33:50,548
I protest.

521
00:33:51,413 --> 00:33:54,263
No more speaking of death and killing.

522
00:33:54,263 --> 00:33:56,994
It is not for us to take this man's life,

523
00:33:56,994 --> 00:33:59,400
or to spill his blood.

524
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:02,067
This man may be guilty of these crimes,

525
00:34:02,067 --> 00:34:04,942
but here he lies under
our feet like an animal,

526
00:34:04,942 --> 00:34:07,445
drugged into insensitivity.

527
00:34:07,445 --> 00:34:10,945
Are to play God in
determining this man's fate?

528
00:34:10,945 --> 00:34:15,052
In defense of this man, he
is not a totally evil person.

529
00:34:15,052 --> 00:34:17,306
I have seen him at
times when he was a warm

530
00:34:17,306 --> 00:34:18,918
and caring person.

531
00:34:18,918 --> 00:34:23,001
Must it be we who play
the roles of executioners?

532
00:34:24,605 --> 00:34:27,337
The Lord above may hold us
accountable if we take justice

533
