01:14:09,022 --> 01:14:11,272
And now, an eye for an eye.

1073
01:14:12,753 --> 01:14:17,357
Do not fear, our heels
high and sharp will strike

1074
01:14:17,357 --> 01:14:19,274
you swiftly as bullets.

1075
01:14:20,207 --> 01:14:24,009
Your death will come
quickly, I assure you.

1076
01:14:24,009 --> 01:14:26,087
- [Landowner] Oh, no.

1077
01:14:26,087 --> 01:14:28,004
- Justice will be done.

1078
01:14:32,047 --> 01:14:36,004
Now ladies of the jury,
take your positions

1079
01:14:36,004 --> 01:14:37,504
for the execution.

1080
01:14:51,391 --> 01:14:55,058
Now ladies of the jury,
take your positions,

1081
01:14:57,294 --> 01:15:01,461
and on the count of three,
drive your spikes deeply

1082
01:15:02,395 --> 01:15:05,062
and with a vengeance, and power.

1083
01:15:07,336 --> 01:15:09,709
- [Landowner] No, please
don't do this to me!

1084
01:15:09,709 --> 01:15:11,539
I don't deserve to die this way.

1085
01:15:11,539 --> 01:15:12,706
Don't do this!

1086
01:15:17,660 --> 01:15:19,191
- One.

1087
01:15:19,191 --> 01:15:21,941
- [Landowner] No, no, no, no, no.

1088
01:15:25,337 --> 01:15:26,170
- Two.

1089
01:15:26,170 --> 01:15:29,601
- [Landowner] No, no, no, please.

1090
01:15:29,601 --> 01:15:30,434
- Three!

1091
